*{{flagicon|GBR}} [[Light Tank Mk VI|Vickers Light Tank Mark VIA]]
*{{flagicon|USA}} [[M3 Stuart]]
*{{flagicon|USA}} [[M3 Lee]] – Grant and Lee variants, some used post-war to 1955, others converted to [[Yeramba]] self-propelled artillery{{sfn|Horner|1995|p=432}}
*{{flagicon|GBR}} [[Matilda II]]
*{{flagicon|AUS}} [[Sentinel tank|Australian Cruiser Tank Mk1 – Sentinel]]
*{{flagicon|USA}} [[Sherman Tank]] – three for trials purposes only
