*{{flagicon|GBR}} [[Centurion tank|Centurion]]
*{{flagicon|GER}} [[Leopard 1]] Main Battle Tank
*{{flagicon|USA}} [[M1 Abrams|M1A1 Abrams AIM]] Main Battle Tank

